COMPOSER
========

#### Instalar Composer globalmente (pre-requisito)
```
$ curl -sS https://getcomposer.org/installer | php
$ sudo mv composer.phar /usr/local/bin/composer
Para fedora, aws EC2
$ ln -s /usr/local/bin/composer /usr/bin/composer
```


